00:01:52.860 --> 00:01:55.410 align:middle line:90%


00:01:55.410 --> 00:01:59.220 align:middle line:84%
But something had
shifted, and I knew

00:01:59.220 --> 00:02:03.780 align:middle line:84%
that if I didn't make a
dramatic change in my life

00:02:03.780 --> 00:02:05.700 align:middle line:90%
that I was going to die.

00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:08.639 align:middle line:84%
And I called my
mother, and I said,

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:11.280 align:middle line:84%
I need to go back
into treatment.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:15.390 align:middle line:84%
And I'd already been in
treatment three or four times.

00:02:15.390 --> 00:02:18.330 align:middle line:90%
All these other times, I left.

00:02:18.330 --> 00:02:21.390 align:middle line:84%
On day 10, I started
to feel great.

00:02:21.390 --> 00:02:22.920 align:middle line:90%
I'm drug-free.

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:24.790 align:middle line:84%
I'm not like any
of these people.

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:26.180 align:middle line:90%
I'm out of here.

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:28.020 align:middle line:84%
And I would pack
up my little bag,

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:31.560 align:middle line:84%
put my little arrogant suit
on, and march myself out

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:34.740 align:middle line:90%
of treatment, and I was free.

00:02:34.740 --> 00:02:37.680 align:middle line:84%
I was going to make
it to the other side.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:42.600 align:middle line:84%
By day 6 or 7, I'd be on the
phone, looking for my drugs,

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:45.270 align:middle line:90%
and end up right back in rehab.

00:02:45.270 --> 00:02:49.050 align:middle line:84%
So instead of running away this
time, I went into the bathroom,

00:02:49.050 --> 00:02:51.630 align:middle line:84%
and I got down on
my hands and knees.

00:02:51.630 --> 00:02:57.090 align:middle line:84%
And I started begging, please
relieve me of this pain.

00:02:57.090 --> 00:03:00.930 align:middle line:84%
Grant me the serenity to accept
the things I cannot change.

00:03:00.930 --> 00:03:03.630 align:middle line:84%
I cannot change my
desire to leave.

00:03:03.630 --> 00:03:06.150 align:middle line:84%
And in that moment,
on that floor,

00:03:06.150 --> 00:03:08.040 align:middle line:90%
something happened to me.

00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:10.690 align:middle line:90%
Something that was like magic.

00:03:10.690 --> 00:03:12.540 align:middle line:90%
It was mind-blowing to me.

00:03:12.540 --> 00:03:15.330 align:middle line:84%
Because all of the sudden,
after a few minutes,

00:03:15.330 --> 00:03:18.380 align:middle line:84%
I knew I could
stay one more day.

00:03:18.380 --> 00:03:22.340 align:middle line:84%
How could I go from
terrified and my mind going

00:03:22.340 --> 00:03:27.710 align:middle line:84%
a million miles a minute to
this place of complete peace?

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:33.260 align:middle line:84%
I walked out of there
on day 28, knowing

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:37.380 align:middle line:84%
that there was something
that I had to find out about.

00:03:37.380 --> 00:03:46.510 align:middle line:90%


00:03:46.510 --> 00:03:48.130 align:middle line:90%
>> The shadow is dark.

00:03:48.130 --> 00:03:49.900 align:middle line:90%
It's secretive.

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:52.010 align:middle line:90%
It can be dangerous.

00:03:52.010 --> 00:03:54.530 align:middle line:84%
>> The shadow is everything
that we don't want other people

00:03:54.530 --> 00:03:55.330 align:middle line:90%
to see.

00:03:55.330 --> 00:03:58.510 align:middle line:84%
>> Things we hide,
things that we lie about.

00:03:58.510 --> 00:04:00.430 align:middle line:84%
Not only to us,
but to ourselves.

00:04:00.430 --> 00:04:02.740 align:middle line:84%
>> And they are the sort
of monsters that come out

00:04:02.740 --> 00:04:05.170 align:middle line:84%
of the caves in the
middle of the night.

00:04:05.170 --> 00:04:09.370 align:middle line:84%
>> It is that dark, intrinsic
side of us that each and every

00:04:09.370 --> 00:04:10.720 align:middle line:90%
one of us tries to hide.

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:13.540 align:middle line:84%
>> Because we've been told from
such an early age that these

00:04:13.540 --> 00:04:15.940 align:middle line:84%
are not acceptable
components of who we are.

00:04:15.940 --> 00:04:17.550 align:middle line:84%
>> To have one
aspect of the soul,

00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:19.675 align:middle line:84%
you have to experience the
other aspect of the soul

00:04:19.675 --> 00:04:20.649 align:middle line:90%
to counterbalance it.

00:04:20.649 --> 00:04:22.750 align:middle line:84%
>> "Hello darkness,
my old friend.

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:24.630 align:middle line:90%
I've come to talk to you again."

00:04:24.630 --> 00:04:26.200 align:middle line:84%
They we're talking
about the shadow.

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:28.810 align:middle line:84%
>> The only time you don't have
a shadow is if you're standing

00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:29.610 align:middle line:90%
in the darkness.

00:04:29.610 --> 00:04:32.910 align:middle line:90%


00:04:32.910 --> 00:04:35.760 align:middle line:84%
>> The shadow shows
up in so many ways.

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:38.610 align:middle line:84%
Writing bad checks,
drinking too much,

00:04:38.610 --> 00:04:41.340 align:middle line:84%
cheating on our tax
returns, dipping

00:04:41.340 --> 00:04:44.400 align:middle line:84%
into our expense account
