00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:55.140 align:middle line:84%
Screaming at our kids or
verbally abusing our partners

00:04:55.140 --> 00:04:59.370 align:middle line:84%
after being the nice guy at work
all day, surfing the internet

00:04:59.370 --> 00:05:03.300 align:middle line:84%
and visiting porn sites while
our wife makes us dinner.

00:05:03.300 --> 00:05:06.000 align:middle line:10%
Cheating on our husband
while he is hard at work,

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.490 align:middle line:10%
trying to provide all
the extra pleasures

00:05:08.490 --> 00:05:10.500 align:middle line:10%
in life for our family.

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:14.950 align:middle line:84%
Stealing our coworkers' ideas
and claiming them as our own.

00:05:14.950 --> 00:05:17.830 align:middle line:84%
The shadow is made up of
the thoughts, emotions,

00:05:17.830 --> 00:05:21.140 align:middle line:84%
and impulses that we find
too painful, embarrassing,

00:05:21.140 --> 00:05:24.420 align:middle line:90%
or distasteful to accept.

00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:28.230 align:middle line:84%
So instead of dealing with
them, we repress them.

00:05:28.230 --> 00:05:30.810 align:middle line:84%
Right now, hundreds
of millions of people

00:05:30.810 --> 00:05:34.330 align:middle line:84%
are living in denial of
their individual shadow,

00:05:34.330 --> 00:05:38.700 align:middle line:84%
and all of us are being affected
by the collective shadow

00:05:38.700 --> 00:05:42.390 align:middle line:84%
in more ways than
we can imagine.

00:05:42.390 --> 00:05:46.500 align:middle line:84%
>> The collective shadow
manifests as evil, as war,

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:49.380 align:middle line:84%
as terrorism, as
social injustice,

00:05:49.380 --> 00:05:53.690 align:middle line:84%
as radical inequities
in our economic status.

00:05:53.690 --> 00:05:57.090 align:middle line:10%
You know, right now, we
have 50% of the world living

00:05:57.090 --> 00:06:02.010 align:middle line:10%
on less than $2 a day,
20% of the world living

00:06:02.010 --> 00:06:03.960 align:middle line:10%
on less than $1 a day.

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:05.960 align:middle line:84%
We are totally in
denial of the fact

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:07.950 align:middle line:84%
that this is also
a manifestation

00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:09.010 align:middle line:90%
of our collective shadow.

00:06:09.010 --> 00:06:09.810 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:06:09.810 --> 00:06:12.990 align:middle line:84%
Because people in
social institutions

00:06:12.990 --> 00:06:16.530 align:middle line:84%
and financial institutions,
political institutions,

00:06:16.530 --> 00:06:19.890 align:middle line:84%
corporate institutions
