00:06:19.890 --> 00:06:21.010 align:middle line:90%
of the shadow energy.

00:06:21.010 --> 00:06:22.260 align:middle line:90%
They don't even understand it.

00:06:22.260 --> 00:06:25.350 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you mean what we
call evil in the world

00:06:25.350 --> 00:06:28.660 align:middle line:84%
