pedophiles in its own clergy.

00:06:54.660 --> 00:06:57.790 align:middle line:84%
These are all expressions
of the shadow.

00:06:57.790 --> 00:07:00.870 align:middle line:84%
>> The entire trajectory of
human history at this point is

00:07:00.870 --> 00:07:01.750 align:middle line:90%
like the "Titanic."

00:07:01.750 --> 00:07:03.360 align:middle line:90%
It is headed for an iceberg.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.622 align:middle line:84%
It is going in a direction
that is unsustainable,

00:07:05.622 --> 00:07:07.080 align:middle line:84%
and it is going in
a direction that

00:07:07.080 --> 00:07:09.050 align:middle line:84%
is unsurvivable if
not for us, then

00:07:09.050 --> 00:07:11.640 align:middle line:84%
at least for our children
or our grandchildren.

00:07:11.640 --> 00:07:13.470 align:middle line:84%
And from an archetypal
perspective,

00:07:13.470 --> 00:07:15.990 align:middle line:84%
each and every one
of us is the captain.

00:07:15.990 --> 00:07:18.880 align:middle line:84%
And the temptation
is, it's too painful.

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:20.756 align:middle line:84%
The temptation is to
just distract ourselves.

00:07:20.756 --> 00:07:22.755 align:middle line:84%
The temptation is to
pretend it's not happening,

00:07:22.755 --> 00:07:24.590 align:middle line:84%
or the temptation is
to go into cynicism,

00:07:24.590 --> 00:07:26.370 align:middle line:84%
or the temptation is
to just go into anger

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:29.250 align:middle line:84%
and indulge that
and not do anything.

00:07:29.250 --> 00:07:32.430 align:middle line:84%
And each and every one of us
are challenged at this point.

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:35.200 align:middle line:84%
Don't be the captain who
just goes downstairs and goes

00:07:35.200 --> 00:07:36.000 align:middle line:90%
to sleep.

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Everything that expands
has got to contract.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.133 align:middle line:90%
What goes up's got to come down.

00:07:39.133 --> 00:07:41.630 align:middle line:84%
People are going to be
confronted with their shadow

00:07:41.630 --> 00:07:42.430 align:middle line:90%
all of the sudden.

00:07:42.430 --> 00:07:44.260 align:middle line:84%
Have been living high,
living wonderful,

00:07:44.260 --> 00:07:46.890 align:middle line:84%
