exorbitantly exuding.

00:07:46.890 --> 00:07:49.380 align:middle line:84%
And now suddenly, there's going
to be a contractive phase.

00:07:49.380 --> 00:07:51.090 align:middle line:84%
And if you haven't
met yourself, if you

00:07:51.090 --> 00:07:54.130 align:middle line:84%
haven't done your self work, if
you haven't been on the inside

00:07:54.130 --> 00:07:56.730 align:middle line:84%
and done some exploration
and cleaned up--

00:07:56.730 --> 00:07:59.110 align:middle line:84%
you know, cleaned your
house and detoxed it,

00:07:59.110 --> 00:08:00.360 align:middle line:90%
you're going to be in trouble.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:05.410 align:middle line:90%


00:08:05.410 --> 00:08:08.830 align:middle line:84%
>> The birth of our shadow
occurs when we are very young,

00:08:08.830 --> 00:08:12.580 align:middle line:84%
before our logical thinking mind
has developed enough to filter

00:08:12.580 --> 00:08:17.410 align:middle line:84%
the messages we receive
from parents, caregivers,

00:08:17.410 --> 00:08:19.090 align:middle line:90%
and the world at large.

00:08:19.090 --> 00:08:21.710 align:middle line:84%
