as horrific experiences,

00:37:12.440 --> 00:37:14.870 align:middle line:84%
terrible experiences,
dark experiences, when

00:37:14.870 --> 00:37:17.540 align:middle line:84%
in truth, they're really
enlightened experiences,

00:37:17.540 --> 00:37:20.630 align:middle line:84%
because they help
us to be who we are.

00:37:20.630 --> 00:37:22.670 align:middle line:84%
They help us to
be compassionate.

00:37:22.670 --> 00:37:24.290 align:middle line:90%
They help us to be forgiving.

00:37:24.290 --> 00:37:26.692 align:middle line:84%
They help us to look at
someone very, very differently.

00:37:26.692 --> 00:37:29.530 align:middle line:90%


00:37:29.530 --> 00:37:31.455 align:middle line:84%
>> What doesn't kill
us makes us stronger.

00:37:31.455 --> 00:37:35.229 align:middle line:90%


00:37:35.229 --> 00:37:37.270 align:middle line:84%
>> At a certain point in
life, it's about saying,

00:37:37.270 --> 00:37:39.061 align:middle line:84%
I have been through
what I've been through.

00:37:39.061 --> 00:37:40.690 align:middle line:84%
I've succeeded in
some ways, perhaps,

00:37:40.690 --> 00:37:42.400 align:middle line:84%
but I've also
failed in some ways.

00:37:42.400 --> 00:37:45.370 align:middle line:84%
I've been strong at times, but
