00:37:45.370 --> 00:37:47.980 align:middle line:84%
I've gotten some things
right, and other things,

00:37:47.980 --> 00:37:48.947 align:middle line:90%
I've gotten wrong.

00:37:48.947 --> 00:37:50.530 align:middle line:84%
And some things have
gone well for me,

00:37:50.530 --> 00:37:53.392 align:middle line:84%
and some things have
