half-Japanese, half-Chinese.

00:39:21.910 --> 00:39:25.870 align:middle line:84%
I was considered mixed
and impure enough

00:39:25.870 --> 00:39:27.700 align:middle line:90%
to be raised in Japan.

00:39:27.700 --> 00:39:29.470 align:middle line:84%
You know, my parents
live in Japan,

00:39:29.470 --> 00:39:33.340 align:middle line:84%
