00:40:56.410 --> 00:40:59.410 align:middle line:84%
So I couldn't be the
leader I am today

00:40:59.410 --> 00:41:02.690 align:middle line:84%
without going
through the emotions,

00:41:02.690 --> 00:41:06.200 align:middle line:84%
and the pain that I went
through my whole life.

00:41:06.200 --> 00:41:10.165 align:middle line:84%
>> If we look deeper, we will
see that we all have a divine

00:41:10.165 --> 00:41:10.965 align:middle line:90%
recipe.

00:41:10.965 --> 00:41:50.680 align:middle line:90%


00:41:50.680 --> 00:41:52.690 align:middle line:84%
