shame about things

00:41:52.690 --> 00:41:54.250 align:middle line:90%
that have happened to us.

00:41:54.250 --> 00:41:56.920 align:middle line:84%
We've all gone through
difficult times.

00:41:56.920 --> 00:42:00.790 align:middle line:84%
We address these issues
so we can quiet our minds,

00:42:00.790 --> 00:42:06.190 align:middle line:84%
heal our bodies, and get
closer to our hearts' desires.

00:42:06.190 --> 00:42:09.970 align:middle line:84%
