the one that he loved

00:42:13.480 --> 00:42:15.594 align:middle line:90%
the most, which was his father.

00:42:15.594 --> 00:42:18.250 align:middle line:90%


00:42:18.250 --> 00:42:20.590 align:middle line:84%
>> My father was your
traditional Mexican man

00:42:20.590 --> 00:42:24.040 align:middle line:84%
in the sense of working
hard, wanting to get ahead,

00:42:24.040 --> 00:42:26.780 align:middle line:84%
