00:43:08.390 --> 00:43:09.890 align:middle line:90%
I did some personal growth work.

00:43:09.890 --> 00:43:12.747 align:middle line:84%
I went inside, looked at the
shame, the guilt, the pain.

00:43:12.747 --> 00:43:13.580 align:middle line:90%
I went through that.

00:43:13.580 --> 00:43:15.270 align:middle line:90%
I healed that.

00:43:15.270 --> 00:43:18.350 align:middle line:84%
And I was able to have that
