00:43:56.680 --> 00:44:00.540 align:middle line:90%


00:44:00.540 --> 00:44:05.160 align:middle line:90%
>> May 22, 1944.

00:44:05.160 --> 00:44:09.090 align:middle line:84%
When I arrived in
