00:44:26.400 --> 00:44:31.500 align:middle line:84%
I asked an inmate, when
will I see my mother?

00:44:31.500 --> 00:44:34.080 align:middle line:84%
And she pointed at the
chimney, and the fire

00:44:34.080 --> 00:44:36.820 align:middle line:90%
