00:44:36.820 --> 00:44:39.930 align:middle line:84%
And she said, you better
talk about your mother

00:44:39.930 --> 00:44:41.120 align:middle line:90%
in past tense.

00:44:41.120 --> 00:44:44.580 align:middle line:90%
She's burning there.

00:44:44.580 --> 00:44:46.750 align:middle line:84%
My sister and I held
each other and said,

00:44:46.750 --> 00:44:48.220 align:middle line:90%
the spirit never dies.

00:44:48.220 --> 00:44:50.160 align:middle line:90%
The spirit never dies.

00:44:50.160 --> 00:44:55.320 align:middle line:84%
I remember that so
vividly even today.

00:44:55.320 --> 00:44:59.190 align:middle line:84%
In Auschwitz, we
didn't know when

00:44:59.190 --> 00:45:03.810 align:middle line:84%
