00:46:09.630 --> 00:46:14.130 align:middle line:84%
So I created the
part in me that I

00:46:14.130 --> 00:46:17.620 align:middle line:84%
was able to still
be in charge of,

00:46:17.620 --> 00:46:21.420 align:middle line:84%
and not allowing anything
that happened externally

00:46:21.420 --> 00:46:23.310 align:middle line:90%
to murder my spirit.

00:46:23.310 --> 00:46:27.410 align:middle line:84%
I remember I said,
if I survive today,

00:46:27.410 --> 00:46:30.180 align:middle line:90%
then tomorrow, I'll be free.

00:46:30.180 --> 00:46:35.260 align:middle line:90%


00:46:35.260 --> 00:46:38.710 align:middle line:84%
>> I remember when Marita
