00:52:23.080 --> 00:52:25.060 align:middle line:90%
noticed a crack in the Buddha.

00:52:25.060 --> 00:52:27.910 align:middle line:84%
Concerned about
damaging the idol,

00:52:27.910 --> 00:52:31.630 align:middle line:84%
the monks decided to wait
a day before continuing

00:52:31.630 --> 00:52:32.980 align:middle line:90%
with their task.

00:52:32.980 --> 00:52:37.600 align:middle line:84%
Later on, one of the monks came
to check on the giant statue.

00:52:37.600 --> 00:52:41.320 align:middle line:84%
He shined his flashlight
over the entire Buddha,

00:52:41.320 --> 00:52:42.880 align:middle line:84%
and when he reached
the crack, he

00:52:42.880 --> 00:52:45.740 align:middle line:84%
saw something
reflected back at him.

00:52:45.740 --> 00:52:50.230 align:middle line:84%
His curiosity aroused, the
monk got a hammer and a chisel

00:52:50.230 --> 00:52:53.290 align:middle line:84%
and began chipping away
at the clay Buddha.

00:52:53.290 --> 00:52:56.770 align:middle line:84%
As he knocked off piece
